content: Just to the right of this ledge, there's a small cave lined with tiny cocoons everywhere, and a few medium-sized cocoons that will burst to reveal ugly looking Minor Amourworms. They can't do too much other than thrash about or lunge (a surprisingly long distance in a short span), but the one you'll want to worry about is the larger cocoon in the middle that holds a Lesser Amourworm.
